						<h2 class="text-md">Chettinad Pepper Chicken (Koli Milagu Masala)</h2>
						<p class="text-sm">
							A signature dish of the South Indian city of Chennai. It’s flavored with
							fennel seeds, curry leaves, and urad dal, the skinned split black
							lentils that are a popular ingredient in southern India.
						</p>
						<a href="/post" class="btn btn-dark-outline">Tamil Nadu</a>
						<a href="/post" class="btn btn-dark-outline">Chicken</a>
						<a href="/post" class="btn btn-dark-outline">Lunch</a>
